Content.bodyText:
Hi Darren,

You provide the source code of this package via bitbucket. I took a look at it and found some great code I might end up re-using in an application. 
There is however one piece of source not included: dll/FergusonMoriyama.Rss.dll.

Are you willing to share that also? If so, that would be great.

Vincent
